text.tspan: The major change here was adding color to the boxes and a dark background. I
felt this was a good step, but that the stroke on connecting lines was too light.
Additionally, I added examples for each decision.
I made the title larger and more eye-catching. I also increased the stroke on the
lines and added icons to reinforce whether a tool belonged on the homepage.
With more time, I would’ve liked to play with a light theme.
